sequenceDiagram
    actor Human
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant T0 as Tier 0 Cache<br/>(SOUL + STACK + HEARTBEAT)
    participant Haiku as Haiku Router
    participant Domains as Domain Docs
    participant Sonnet as Sonnet Builder
    participant QA as /qa + /browse
    participant Vercel
    participant Store as app-store/STORE.md

    Human->>CC: "Jain menu app — weather, novelty, pricing,<br/>YT videos, share with cook"

    CC->>T0: read (cached ~70 effective tokens)
    T0-->>CC: identity + environment index loaded

    CC->>Haiku: classify domains from brief
    Note over Haiku: Brief has: UI, scoring logic,<br/>external APIs, LLM calls, deploy
    Haiku-->>CC: load → design, coding, llm,<br/>knowledge, deployment, analytics

    CC->>Domains: load 6 domain docs (on-demand)
    Domains-->>CC: patterns, connectors, stack choices

    CC->>CC: fill PROGRAM.md<br/>(brief, persona, constraints, success criteria)
    CC->>Human: PROGRAM.md ready — confirm?
    Human-->>CC: confirmed

    CC->>Sonnet: write BUILD.md spec
    Note over Sonnet: App name, routes, components,<br/>API routes, connectors, env vars
    Sonnet-->>CC: BUILD.md written

    CC->>Human: BUILD.md ready — review spec
    Human-->>CC: approved

    CC->>Human: visual approval gate<br/>(design direction: A/B/C/D?)
    Human-->>CC: Direction A — Quiet Mandala, warm tones

    CC->>Sonnet: build code per BUILD.md
    Note over Sonnet: React + Vite + Sandy tokens<br/>Vercel Functions for scoring API

    CC->>QA: /qa — navigate, interact, verify
    QA-->>CC: issues found (if any) → fix loop
    CC->>QA: rerun until pass

    CC->>Vercel: /ship → deploy
    Vercel-->>CC: live URL

    CC->>Store: append row to STORE.md
    CC->>Human: done ✓<br/>URL + store entry
